{"tid":588713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA球星打香港甲二？ 傳前湖人中鋒拜林加盟建龍","createTime":"2018-03-11T11:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T03:16:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a95f7cddb656f47bfd6036aa7270d11c3a26238","tid":588713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cbsla.files.wordpress.com/2011/05/kobe_bynum_88060780.jpg?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsla.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F05%2Fkobe_bynum_88060780.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26crop%3D1&h=debe72ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港籃壇將有大引援？盛傳前湖人中鋒拜林（Andrew Bynum）將登陸香港，加盟甲二建龍。如傳聞屬實，他勢成香港籃壇史上名氣最響球星！<br />\n<br />\n現年30歲的拜林於湖人出道和成名，兩奪NBA總冠軍，惟他近年因傷患和個人問題消失於球壇，2014年離開溜馬後無班可落。今次突然傳出他來港進軍甲二的消息，香港籃壇中人透露傳聞日久，不少人皆知悉並非常期待，而建龍隊長區年樂回覆本報記者查詢時則表示「所有事情都未落實」。甲二建龍由李達誠執教，年初於籃總盃分組賽一勝兩負，未能晉級淘汰賽。<br />\n拜林昂藏2米13，他於2005年NBA第十順位被湖人選中，與拜恩(Kobe Bryant)、加素(Pau Gasol)等巨星並肩作戰，平步青雲，助湖人09和10年兩奪NBA總冠軍，2012年他更大顯身價，場均錄得18.7分和11.8個籃板，該年入選全明星隊之餘亦獲選入NBA第二最佳陣容。"},{"pid":"7508c55d3005556d2f839351a268a2c89128b1d5","tid":588713,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff24090d036c19dee514fc0cb4c711a831b7fb6c","tid":588713,"uid":57962,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc45d46540a40d6db400c8f7276212ca0fa91848","tid":588713,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"科撚都三張嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d3f00aef